===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-both|toffee}}
{{wikipedia}}
#{{uncountable}} a type of [[confectionery]] made by boiling [[sugar]] (or [[treacle]], etc) with [[butter]] or [[milk]], then [[cool]]ing the mixture so that it becomes hard
#{{countable}} a small, [[individual]] piece of toffee
#:''a box of toffees''

